8.1 AR

    • kNi
  • ARlocally stationary AR model
    • i[\(n_{i0}, n_{n1}\)]\(n_{i0}, n_{i1}\) \[ n_{i0} = \sum\limits_{j=1}^{i-1}N_{j} + 1\\ n_{i1} = \sum\limits_{j=1}^{i}N_{j} \]
    • jynAR
    • AR
    • AICAR
